            <p>As part of our celebration of National Volunteer Week, Hospice Niagara is once again treating its volunteers to a day-long retreat to show our appreciation for all that you do. This is a day of self-care for our prized volunteers who give so much of yourselves to those for whom you care</p>
            <p>The theme this year is “Refresh!”  We are delighted to have Colleen Falco as our Keynote Speaker.  Colleen, a Hospice Niagara Board Member, is the HR Director at Niagara Casinos.  Colleen’s presentation, entitled “Refresh Your Spirit”, invites you to step away from your daily stresses and obligations to visit the most important person in your life….you!</p>
